### 1. Vektory **a = (2, 3)** a **b = (-6, 9)**

 × b = | i j k | | 2 3 0 | | -6 9 0 |

a × b = i(3 * 0 - 0 * 9) - j(2 * 0 - 0 * (-6)) + k(2 * 9 - 3 * (-6)) = i(0) - j(0) + k(18 + 18) = 0i - 0j + 36k = (0, 0, 36)

b × a = -a × b = (0, 0, -36)

|a| = √(2² + 3²) = √(4 + 9) = √13

|b| = √((-6)² + 9²) = √(36 + 81) = √117

|a · b| = |15| = 15

|a × b| = √(0² + 0² + 36²) = √1296 = 36


---

### 2. Vektory **a = (3, 3)** a **b = (0, 0, 1)**

a · b = 3 * 0 + 3 * 0 + 0 * 1 = 0

a × b = | i j k | | 3 3 0 | | 0 0 1 |

a × b = i(3 * 1 - 0 * 0) - j(3 * 1 - 0 * 0) + k(3 * 0 - 3 * 0) = i(3) - j(3) + k(0) = (3, -3, 0)

b × a = -a × b = (-3, 3, 0)

|a| = √(3² + 3²) = √(9 + 9) = √18 = 3√2

|b| = √(0² + 0² + 1²) = √1 = 1

|a · b| = |0| = 0

|a × b| = √(3² + (-3)² + 0²) = √(9 + 9) = √18 = 3√2


---

### 3. Vektory **a = (9, 3)** a **b = (3, 1)**

a · b = 9 * 3 + 3 * 1 = 27 + 3 = 30

a × b = | i j k | | 9 3 0 | | 3 1 0 |

a × b = i(3 * 0 - 0 * 1) - j(9 * 0 - 0 * 3) + k(9 * 1 - 3 * 3) = i(0) - j(0) + k(9 - 9) = (0, 0, 0)

b × a = -a × b = (0, 0, 0)

|a| = √(9² + 3²) = √(81 + 9) = √90 = 3√10

|b| = √(3² + 1²) = √(9 + 1) = √10

|a · b| = |30| = 30

|a × b| = √(0² + 0² + 0²) = √0 = 0



